weigh
Discworld player help
weigh

.SH Name
.SI 5
weigh - estimate the weight of something
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
weigh <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Weigh will let you guess the weight of an object you are carrying with
an accuracy dependent on your dexterity.  For an accurate determination,
you will need to find a balance or weighing machine somewhere.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> weigh backpack
You heft the small backpack and guess that it weighs about twenty pounds.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
look
.EP
